In this repo there are the softwares for the course "physiology of perception".

The software physio_psth-1.21-qt3update was gross coversion to make it work with qt4.
The software physio_psthqt4 is a final qt4 conversion bug free
The software physio_stim-0.5.3 contains few improvements from the previous version.

Dependecies:
libqt4-dev
libqwt4c2
libqt4-qt3support - Qt 3 compatibility library for Qt 4 
libcomedi-dev - Development library for Comedi
libcomedi0 - Library for Comedi

